data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home located in the beautiful golf community of Sherman Hills. This home features a  spacious living room, split bedroom floor plan, and a kitchen and dining area with plenty of room for entertaining. Outside you will find a covered patio area where you can sit back, enjoy the golf course view and Florida living at its finest. This home is priced to sell and is waiting on your finishing touches to make it your own, so call today to schedule your personal showing.  This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee).
